==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Revivalist
<hw>Re*viv"al*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A clergyman or layman who
promotes revivals of religion; an advocate for religious revivals;
sometimes, specifically, a clergyman, without a particular charge, who
goes about to promote revivals. Also used adjectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Revivalistic</ent>⟦br⟧
